name: 1private beautiful bedroom in Boston #1
neighborhood_overview: It’s a quite neighborhood; easy accessible by transportation, Uber, foot.
description:
This is a 4bedroom house in Boston, South End; 5 mins walk to Northeastern, 15 mins walk to Boston Medical, 30 minutes walk to Brigham & Women’s Hospital. You have your 1 private bedroom with a lock and can share the kitchen, living room, washer/dryer, patio, 1 1/2 baths with other guests. It has 1queen bed, a closet, a desk, shelves, and can accommodate up to 2 guests. Everything is professionally clean after the guests leave.

The space
This place is 15 minutes Uber ride to Fenway, Copley Place, Downtown Boston. Northeastern University is 5 minutes walk. It is also accessible by transportation or by foot. For example it can take up to 25 minutes by foot to go to Copley Place.

Guest access
Guests will share kitchen, living room, washer/dryer, patio for entertainment or grilling.

Other things to note
Please respect other guests privacy.
